<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n11025b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n11" href="#n11025b">N11 (VI.B.5)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n11all.htm#n11025b"> 25(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> S John of Patmos ~ </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: That is, St John the Evangelist. He was believed to have been banished to Patmos by the Romans and to have written the Apocalypse or Book of Revelation there. See Revelation 21:1: And I saw a new heaven and a new earth: for the first heaven and the first earth were passed away; and there was no more sea. </mm> </dd></dl>
